            <title>[CASSANDRA-6103] ConcurrentModificationException in TokenMetadata.cloneOnlyTokenMap</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6103</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
